{"type":"message","id":"bcb0a293","parentId":"c54b9968","timestamp":"2026-03-15T11:58:57.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger wants me to update the skill with the corrected distributed deployment solution. Let me update the SKILL.md file with the correct information about multi-server deployment.","thinkingSignature":"074e6112d88849158f78be989e75f6dbe2f89496872252e80d7379b7e166e2ea"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gnccigjycxpj_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\single-group-multi-bot\\SKILL.md","newText":"## 🔄 扩展场景\n\n### 场景一：同一服务器多Bot（当前方案）\n- 所有Bot运行在同一台服务器的同一个OpenClaw实例\n- 通过不同的飞书应用区分Bot\n- Gateway使用单一端口（默认18789）\n\n### 场景二：不同服务器多Bot（分布式部署）\n\n```\n服务器A (本机)          服务器B                   服务器C\n┌─────────────┐       ┌─────────────┐           ┌─────────────┐\n│ IT工程师     │       │ 网站开发    │           │ 光储系统    │\n│ OpenClaw    │       │ OpenClaw   │           │ OpenClaw   │\n│ 端口:18789  │       │ 端口:18789  │           │ 端口:18789  │\n└──────┬──────┘       └──────┬──────┘           └──────┬──────┘\n       │                     │                     │\n       └─────────────────────┼─────────────────────┘\n                             ▼\n                    ┌─────────────────┐\n                    │   飞书群聊      │\n                    │  多Bot共存     │\n                    └─────────────────┘\n```\n\n#### 关键点：端口配置\n- **不同服务器**：每台可以用相同端口（通过IP区分）\n- **同一服务器多实例**：必须用不同端口\n\n#### 部署步骤：\n\n1. **每台服务器安装OpenClaw**\n```bash\nnpm install -g openclaw\nopenclaw init\n```\n\n2. **每台服务器创建独立飞书应用**\n   - 访问飞书开放平台\n   - 每个应用独立App ID和App Secret\n   - 权限：im:message:send_as_bot\n\n3. **配置各服务器OpenClaw**\n```json\n// 服务器A (IT工程师)\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [{\n      \"id\": \"it-engineer\",\n      \"identity\": \"🔧 IT工程师\",\n      \"workspace\": \"~\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\it-engineer\"\n    }]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"appId\": \"cli_xxx_a\",\n      \"appSecret\": \"xxx_a\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n// 服务器B (网站开发)\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [{\n      \"id\": \"web-developer\",\n      \"identity\": \"🌐 网站开发工程师\",\n      \"workspace\": \"~\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\web-developer\"\n    }]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"appId\": \"cli_xxx_b\", \n      \"appSecret\": \"xxx_b\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n4. **各服务器启动Gateway**\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n每台服务器使用默认端口18789即可（端口通过IP区分）\n\n5. **将所有Bot添加到同一飞书群**\n   - 在群设置中添加各个飞书应用机器人\n   - 各Bot通过@提及触发响应","oldText":"## 🔄 扩展场景\n\n### 添加新Bot\n1. 在飞书开放平台创建新应用\n2. 在openclaw.json添加新Agent配置\n3. 重新启动Gateway\n\n### Bot职责调整\n修改对应Agent工作空间的`SOUL.md`即可。"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":783,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":31611,"totalTokens":32430,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0009396,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0037933199999999998,"total":0.00474372}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773575913458}}
