\",\n+260       \"workspace\": \"~\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\it-engineer\"\n+261     }]\n+262   },\n+263   \"channels\": {\n+264     \"feishu\": {\n+265       \"appId\": \"cli_xxx_a\",\n+266       \"appSecret\": \"xxx_a\"\n+267     }\n+268   }\n+269 }\n+270 \n+271 // 服务器B (网站开发)\n+272 {\n+273   \"agents\": {\n+274     \"list\": [{\n+275       \"id\": \"web-developer\",\n+276       \"identity\": \"🌐 网站开发工程师\",\n+277       \"workspace\": \"~\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\web-developer\"\n+278     }]\n+279   },\n+280   \"channels\": {\n+281     \"feishu\": {\n+282       \"appId\": \"cli_xxx_b\", \n+283       \"appSecret\": \"xxx_b\"\n+284     }\n+285   }\n+286 }\n+287 ```\n+288 \n+289 4. **各服务器启动Gateway**\n+290 ```bash\n+291 openclaw gateway start\n+292 ```\n+293 每台服务器使用默认端口18789即可（端口通过IP区分）\n+294 \n+295 5. **将所有Bot添加到同一飞书群**\n+296    - 在群设置中添加各个飞书应用机器人\n+297    - 各Bot通过@提及触发响应\n+298 \n 220 ---\n 221 \n 222 **技能版本**: v1.0  \n 223 **创建时间**: 2026-03-15  \n     ...","firstChangedLine":212},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773575937562}}
