{"type":"message","id":"b1f11e2e","parentId":"5b87c382","timestamp":"2026-03-15T11:59:07.319Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Let me provide a summary to Roger.","thinkingSignature":"21b88ed7edff5caec8967ebcdfa238a2879cd1dde09a6ea12df43a142bf43c6a"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已更新方案，新增**跨服务器分布式部署**完整方案：\n\n## 方案一（更新版）：多服务器独立部署\n\n### 架构图\n```\n服务器A              服务器B              服务器C\n┌─────────┐        ┌─────────┐        ┌─────────┐\n│ IT工程师 │        │ 网站开发 │        │ 光储系统 │\n│ 端口18789│        │ 端口18789│        │ 端口18789│\n└────┬────┘        └────┬────┘        └────┬────┘\n     │                   │                   │\n     └───────────────────┼───────────────────┘\n                         ▼\n                ┌──────────────┐\n                │   飞书群聊    │\n                │  多Bot共存   │\n                └──────────────┘\n```\n\n### 核心要点\n| 项目 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 端口 | 每台服务器可用相同端口（18789），通过IP区分 |\n| 飞书应用 | 每个Bot独立应用（不同App ID） |\n| 消息路由 | 群聊中@对应Bot触发响应 |\n\n### 部署步骤（简版）\n1. 每台服务器安装OpenClaw\n2. 每台服务器配置独立飞书应用\n3. 各服务器启动Gateway（默认端口）\n4. 将所有Bot添加到同一飞书群\n\n已同步更新到skill文档 ✓"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":15903,"output":309,"cacheRead":16692,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32904,"cost":{"input":0.0047709,"output":0.00037079999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0005007599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00564246}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773575940631}}
{"type":"message","id":"f864a9d0","parentId":"b1f11e2e","timestamp":"2026-03-15T13:47:13.074Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b545fcb34d8a4c4f61fe08a9f1c3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_e889ee1e558f98e299f7646d81c0152d\",\n  \"sender\": \"Roger\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-15 21:47 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_e889ee1e558f98e299f7646d81c0152d\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"history_count\": 2\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Roger (ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9\",\n  \"name\": \"Roger\"\n}\n```\n\nChat history since last reply (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773582267860,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: <at user_id=\\\"ou_9a56a8f09c7737ee6a387dd3bdd22a06\\\">A-IT工程师</at> 介绍自己\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773582389195,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: 如何配置另一台服务器上的openclaw，是他的agent也能在群组里\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b545fcb34d8a4c4f61fe08a9f1c3]\nRoger: 如何配置另一台服务器上的openclaw，是它的agent也能在群组里交流\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_f75fa2e77e5d7651f90be461a4fb2104\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1773582433065}}
{"type":"message","id":"e098c1a1","parentId":"f864a9d0","timestamp":"2026-03-15T13:47:26.484Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger asks how to configure OpenClaw on another server so that its agent can also communicate in the group chat. This is the distributed deployment scenario we just discussed. Let me provide a clear, step-by-step guide.","thinkingSignature":"54bbb837118dc29de6592d75a98342d1d4ad2607f0106fb13748d17197052e27"},{"type":"text","text":"## 跨服务器部署步骤\n\n### 前提条件\n- 服务器A（已有）：运行IT工程师Bot，已加入群聊\n- 服务器B（新装）：需要加入另一个Bot到同一群聊\n\n### 步骤1：在服务器B安装OpenClaw\n\n```bash\n# 安装\nnpm install -g openclaw\n\n# 初始化\nopenclaw init\n```\n\n### 步骤2：在服务器B创建飞书应用\n\n1. 打开 [飞书开放平台](https://open.feishu.cn/)\n2. 创建新应用（如：OpenClaw-WebDev）\n3. 获取 **App ID** 和 **App Secret**\n4. 添加权限：`im:message:send_as_bot`、`im:message:send_as_common_bot`\n5. 发布版本\n\n### 步骤3：在服务器B创建Agent\n\n```bash\n# 创建工作空间\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace/agents/web-developer\n```\n\n创建 `SOUL.md`、`AGENTS.md` 等身份文件（参考IT工程师的配置）\n\n### 步骤4：配置服务器B的openclaw.json\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [{\n      \"id\": \"web-developer\",\n      \"identity\": \"🌐 网站开发工程师\",\n      \"workspace\": \"~\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\web-developer\"\n    }]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"appId\": \"cli_服务器B的App_ID\",\n      \"appSecret\": \"服务器B的App_Secret\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 步骤5：启动Gateway\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n### 步骤6：将新Bot添加到群聊\n\n1. 在飞书群聊设置中点击\"添加成员\"\n2. 搜索并添加服务器B的新飞书应用\n3. 完成！\n\n### 关键点\n\n| 项目 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 端口 | 两台服务器可用相同端口（18789），通过IP区分 |\n| 飞书应用 | 每个服务器用独立应用（不同App ID） |\n| 群聊 | 多个应用Bot加入同一群 |\n\n**需要我给出更详细的某一步骤吗？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":507,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":33350,"totalTokens":33893,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0006083999999999999,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0040019999999999995,"total":0.0046212}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773582433070}}
