{"type":"message","id":"fbaa4752","parentId":"c10913c8","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:07:14.758Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger is asking if the other bots in the group can talk to each other. This is an interesting question about bot-to-bot communication.\n\nLet me explain: The different bots running on different servers are independent of each other. They each have their own OpenClaw instance and are connected to different Feishu apps. They don't have a direct communication channel between them.\n\nHowever, I can act as a bridge if needed - I can receive messages and forward them to other bots through various means (like API calls, sessions_spawn, etc.).\n\nBut the key point is: bot-to-bot direct communication is not automatic. They would need some kind of middleware or orchestration layer to talk to each other.","thinkingSignature":"7ab3872b6cb863314ec5409b331bb54ac9686cf9dbba0c1bfdeeb6b977734286"},{"type":"text","text":"不能直接相互对话。\n\n## 原因\n\n每个Bot运行在**独立服务器**上，有独立的OpenClaw实例：\n```\n服务器A                 服务器B                 服务器C\n┌─────────┐            ┌─────────┐            ┌─────────┐\n│ 网站开发 │            │ 光储系统 │            │  IT工程师 │\n│ Agent  │            │ Agent  │            │ Agent  │\n└────┬────┘            └────┬────┘            └────┬────┘\n     │                      │                      │\n     ▼                      ▼                      ▼\n  飞书应用A               飞书应用B               飞书应用C\n     │                      │                      │\n     └──────────────────────┼──────────────────────┘\n                            ▼\n                    同一飞书群聊\n```\n\n- 每个Bot只响应被@的消息\n- Bot之间**没有内置通信机制**\n- 各Bot独立运行，互不可见\n\n## 如果需要Bot协作\n\n可以通过**我作为中转**：\n1. 用户@网站开发工程师问光储问题\n2. 我（IT工程师）收到后，可以调用其他工具/服务获取答案\n3. 或者让用户直接@光储系统工程师\n\n需要我实现某种协作机制吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":403,"cacheRead":9177,"cacheWrite":27721,"totalTokens":37337,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0004836,"cacheRead":0.00027530999999999996,"cacheWrite":0.00332652,"total":0.00409623}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773583621449}}
